---
title: Quick Mediterranean Beef & Haloumi Burger with Caramelised Onion, Truffle Mayo & Pear Salad
description: We’re so excited about this burger, with crispy chunks of squeaky level-one haloumi, creamy truffle mayo and a side of fresh pear salad. Let’s just say, you won’t need the local pub’s menu on hand when you’ve got this recipe under your belt.
